{
  "stem": "1415.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she asked me if it would be OK for her to take me to see the lager eldester, which is the head of the camp, the Jewish head of the camp.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And now, there was another privileged person, and I said, sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So just before she took me to see-- I'm talking about time elapsing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It didn't happen like, today, and later and-- it happened during time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm talking about time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when we got there, none of us did anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- we got up in the morning, we went to appel.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When, at the crack of dawn, we would have appel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we would stand in appel, and as I was saying, I learned how-- where to stand, even though we had our own designated spot, and we had to stand in our own designated spot.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had found my designated spot to be in the middle, and not at the end, and not in the back, and not at the front.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at every appel, somebody would get a beating.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somebody didn't stand right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Somebody didn't do whatever it was that had to be done.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we would stand there until a German-- a German would come by, and it used to be women.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In our block, at least, there was a woman that would come by, and she was dressed just like any other officer, and with those clanking of the boots, and she would go with her poke, and count us.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The same way as our block eldester would count, previously.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She would make sure everybody's there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and-- and the German, she would tell the German, everybody's here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But most of the time, she would count us again, the German officer.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
